# Delta Learn Frontend

React 19 + Vite 8 SPA consuming the Django REST backend.

## Architecture

```
src/
├── api/client.js           # API functions + JWT token management
├── context/
│   ├── ThemeContext.jsx     # Dark mode (persisted, no toggle in UI)
│   └── AuthContext.jsx      # JWT auth state, login/register/logout
├── components/
│   ├── HomePage.jsx        # Subject cards
│   ├── ChapterView.jsx     # Chapter renderer, highlighting, Ctrl+Z undo
│   ├── Sidebar.jsx         # Chapter navigation
│   ├── MermaidDiagram.jsx  # Client-side Mermaid rendering
│   ├── AuthModal.jsx       # Login/register (Portal → body)
│   ├── HighlightPopup.jsx  # Color picker for highlights
│   ├── NotesDrawer.jsx     # Side-by-side notes panel (shifts main content)
│   ├── HighlightsPage.jsx  # All user highlights
│   ├── SubscribePage.jsx   # DeltaMails subscription
│   └── DeltaSpinner.jsx    # Animated triangle loader
├── App.jsx                 # Router + SubjectPage + UserButton
├── App.css                 # All styles (single file, dark theme)
└── main.jsx                # Entry with BrowserRouter
```

## Routes

| Path | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| `/` | HomePage | Subject cards |
| `/highlights` | HighlightsPage | User highlights |
| `/subscribe` | SubscribePage | DeltaMails form |
| `/:subject/chapter/:id` | SubjectPage | Sidebar + ChapterView |
| `/:subject` | SubjectRedirect | → chapter/1 |

## API Client (`src/api/client.js`)

- `BASE_URL` from `VITE_API_URL`, default `http://localhost:8000/api`
- `apiFetch()`: auto-attaches JWT Bearer, auto-refreshes on 401
- Tokens in `localStorage` key `delta_tokens`

### Functions (21)
- Public: `fetchSubjects`, `fetchSubjectDetail`, `fetchChapter`
- Auth: `register`, `login`, `logout`, `fetchMe`, `isLoggedIn`
- Highlights: `fetchHighlights`, `createHighlight`, `updateHighlight`, `deleteHighlight`
- Notes: `fetchNotes`, `createNote`, `updateNote`, `deleteNote`, `analyzeNote`
- DeltaMails: `fetchSubscriptions`, `subscribeDeltaMails`, `updateSubscriptionPreferences`, `unsubscribeDeltaMails`

## Design

- Apple-inspired dark theme (no light/dark toggle in UI)
- CSS custom properties: `--accent` set per-subject dynamically
- Subject colors: System Design #0a84ff, DSA #30d158, AI #ff9f0a
- `DeltaSpinner`: rotating triangle SVG loader used across all loading states
- NotesDrawer: flexbox side-by-side (shifts main content, no overlay/blur)

## Conventions

- `SubjectPage` fetches data, passes props down; `Sidebar`/`ChapterView` are display-only
- `AuthModal` uses `createPortal(jsx, document.body)` to avoid stacking context issues
- Highlights: text selection → auto-save → Ctrl+Z undo via delete API
- Authenticated features: check `useAuth().user`, show "Sign In" for anon

## Deployment

- Netlify: `npm run build` → `dist/`, SPA via `public/_redirects`
- Set `VITE_API_URL` env var to PythonAnywhere backend URL
